1. *Ideju* da se udružimo i radimo zajedno dobili smo od njih. (We got the idea to unite and work together from them.)

2. Imali smo prelepu *ideju*, ali nismo uspeli da je ostvarimo. (We had a beautiful idea, but we weren't able to realize it.)

3. Ona je imala sjajnu *ideju* da učini nešto što niko nije do sada. (She had a brilliant idea to do something that nobody has done before.)

4. Njihova *ideja* je bila da promovešu slobodno tržište. (Their idea was to promote free market.)

5. Njegova *ideja* je bila zaista nerealna. (His idea was really unrealistic.)